#- 1. Why The Ancaps exist.§0
§0
§0Long, long ago. Ttk made a server called 'ancapminecraft'.§0
§0It was a server created because ttk was getting bullied by leftists server hosts.§0
§0
§0
§0

#- Ancapminecraft was a Haven for all edgy teenagers that hate equality and actual liberty.§0
§0
§0Notorious ancaps that joined this server are Joshua97367 and FoxmcLeod.§0
§0
§0
§0

#- Then a prophet of freedom and solidarity joined ancapminecraft.§0
§0They started a guild of solidarity and equality called "The LibSoc Guild"§0
§0
§0Ttk was baffeled and coaxed that some leftist pussy could come over to his server.§0

#- The LibSoc Guild ruined his server.§0
§0And ttk used...§0
§0
§0... the terminal.§0
§0
§0And CivCraft was born.§0
§0
§0
§0
§0
§0
§0

#- 2. The Free Baby Market§0
§0
§0The Ancaps didn't spread much in the beginning of CivCraft, they made a vagina shaft called 'The Rift'.§0
§0
§0The Ancap virus was contianed, and all was well.§0
§0

#- Some Leftist freedom fighters decided to get rid of the oppression and racism once and for all.§0
§0They burned The Rift and destroyed the Ancaps menace.§0
§0
§0People thought the Ancap virus had been eradicated, but it was far from that...§0

#- The Ancaps spread to once free cities such as Columbia and Augusta, and destroyed them from inside out.§0
§0
§0Foofed "Gatzy" Timmyius went into the democratic leftist parliament and dissolved it.§0
§0

#- Oppression and racism ran rampant, and then the Free Baby Market started.§0
§0
§0The Free Baby Market consists of inner hierarchies.§0
§0
§0
§0
§0
§0

#- The Hierarchies are:§0
§0
§01. Foofed§0
§02. Matticus_Fucking_Rex§0
