#- Foofed rules the§0
§0Free Baby Market with an iron fist and a golden penis, where all the penis towers are modeled after.§0
§0The Free Baby Market is made to oppress free, leftist people. And make people racist and hateful.§0
§0
§0

#- The Free Baby Markets sells Babies that are stolen from leftist parents, those who want to teach their children actual freedom and solidarity.§0
§0
