#- 2a. The Monopoly on Force and Justice§0
§0
§0The Ancaps hate freedom, even though they act like they want personal freedom.§0
§0They disregard legitamite state rules and just run into free, sovreign nations and torment their inhabitants.§0

#- They kill anybody trying to interfere with their "justice" and then they tell everybody that they are against "Monopolies on Force"§0
§0but they kill everybody without care.§0
§0They know who to not kill by using their secret device;§0

#- 3. The CKC§0
§0
§0The CKC is a cesspool of crime and corruption, it's where the Ancaps go to oppress free, beautiful people.§0
§0They talk to eachother about the definition of definition and air, and how to oppress leftists more evil.§0

#- In their free time The CKC likes to go to Hitlercon, a great convention for people who love oppression and hate.§0
§0
§0One can usually find Ancaps sitting in the CKC defining definitions.§0
§0
§0

#- 4. The Ancap rag AKA§0
§0"The Pylon"§0
§0
§0The CKC hired Tactful, a notorious ancap and babykiller, to make jokes and write a "legitamite" newspaper.§0
§0Much like RevSci, except more oppressive and priviliged.§0
§0

#- Tactful soon became one of the most privileged Ancap of all the Ancaps, the Upper-Admin Foofed made him an admin personally.§0
§0
